gned. A similar lower bound of $\\Omega(k^2 \\log n/ \\log k)$ is\nknown for incoherent matrices.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 3 Mar 2019 21:33:05 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 27 Jul 2019 21:01:40 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 7 May 2020 11:58:08 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-05-08"}
