iscuss possible\napplications, with a particular focus on the growth of multifuncional\nstructures with stacking layers of different porosity.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 3 Mar 2019 22:49:09 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-03-05"}
