ssibility\nof global and bounded, in the case that ${\\bf\\kappa\\equiv0}$ and $\\alpha>0$. In\ncomparison to the result for the corresponding fluid-free system, the {\\bf\noptimal condition} on the parameter $\\alpha$ for both {\\bf global existence}\nand {\\bf boundedness} are obtained.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 4 Mar 2019 01:25:08 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 5 Mar 2019 03:45:39 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 6 Mar 2019 12:02:04 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Thu, 7 Mar 2019 10:44:06 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-03-08"}
