 triggers shock\nformation in the non-linear stage, and how the weak-beam instability reforms\nand transmits the shock afterwards. The micro-instabilities that we study here\ncould largely contribute to shock triggering as well as to the reformation and\ntransmission of the shock itself.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 4 Mar 2019 10:59:47 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-03-19"}
