 discuss how to generalize our approach to\ngeneral semi-algebraic formulas.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 4 Mar 2019 15:04:09 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 5 Mar 2019 13:38:51 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 11 May 2020 03:56:34 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-05-12"}
